data.name: Label49.Text
data.value:
CONTROL DEVICES Change state of the devices by clicking their pictures in the floorplan.
MODES Use quick modes by clicking them on the top right.
SETTINGS If you want to change password, temperature unit or language you can do this by clicking 'Settings' on the bottom left.
FAVOURITES Add currrent state of the house to the modes bar by clicking 'Add favourite' on the bottom right.
EMERGENCY In case of emergency click red emergency button. Remember that you have to confirm the click before alarm to the authorities is sent.
